firmed earlier syrian reports of a partial israeli mobilization the jordanians would reconnoiter and would reinforce west jordan if it appeared that israel intended to carry out operations against jordan comment the reported israeli moves in the jerusalem area may reflect a limited mobilization there military police have been used to summon army reserves in recent covert mobilizations israel had undertaken limited mobilization were not substantiated by the us army attach in israel as of 11 february and both the syrians and the jordanians have exhibited considerable nervousness over israeli intentions additional french-built jet fighters have recently arrived in israel and command echelons of israeli units on the jordanian border are believed to be in high state of readiness", "unred_source_page": 5}
